    public class BmsGui
extends org.jfree.ui.ApplicationFrame
implements java.lang.Runnable, StartAndStop
    Font-end (gui) of BMS - ~spreadsheet with race data values and dialog to get more info (i.e DataFrame) - chart with total tension of battery (i.e ChartFrame) - text area with errors (i.e ErrorsAreaFrame)
